                <div class="sw-review-card p-4 h-100">
                    <div class="sw-rating mb-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3">"As a busy professional, SmartWash saves me so much time. Express service is a lifesaver — same day delivery talaga! Highly recommended."</p>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="sw-review-avatar">JR</div>
                        <div>
                            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-0 small">Juan Reyes Jr.</h6>
                            <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:0.75rem;"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i> Quezon City</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="sw-review-card p-4 h-100">
                    <div class="sw-rating mb-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-3">"Affordable prices and top-notch quality. My family's laundry is always fresh. Reliable rider din! Will never go back to doing laundry myself."</p>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="sw-review-avatar">AG</div>
                        <div>
                            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-0 small">Ana Garcia Lim</h6>
                            <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:0.75rem;"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i> Pasig City</span>
                        </div>
