            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-4 sw-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-3 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="sw-trust-badge justify-content-center">
                    <i class="bi bi-leaf fs-5 text-success"></i>
                    <span>Eco-Certified Detergents</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="sw-trust-badge justify-content-center">
                    <i class="bi bi-patch-check-fill fs-5 text-primary"></i>
                    <span>Licensed Business</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="sw-trust-badge justify-content-center">
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill fs-5 text-warning"></i>
                    <span>5-Star Rated Service</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="sw-cta-banner">
    <div class="container text-center position-relative" style="z-index:2;">
        <h2 class="text-white fw-bold display-6 mb-3">Ready for Fresh Laundry?</h2>
        <p class="text-white opacity-75 mb-4 mx-auto" style="max-width:480px;">Let us handle the dirty work. Book your first order today and enjoy freshly cleaned, perfectly folded clothes.</p>
        <a href="/Order/Place" class="sw-btn sw-btn-white px-5 py-3 fs-6">
            <i class="bi bi-basket-fill"></i> Book Now — It's Easy
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5 sw-section-alt">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <span class="sw-section-badge"><i class="bi bi-heart"></i> Why SmartWash?</span>
